Program: Outlook
Title: Cuban Custody Battle
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrgx
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A visit to the home town of Elián González, the Cuban boy in the custody battle which has huge political ramifications for relations between USA and Cuba. Also, the problem of providing appropriate food aid when dealing with the world's malnutrition problems. Finally, keeping pigeons dominates one man's life in Azerbaijan. Presenter: Heather Payton. Show less